    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example, centered around the high-revving S54 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Critical preventive maintenance is complete, including rear subframe reinforcement and a recent rod bearing service. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a front strut tower brace. While minor cosmetic patina exists, the mechanical synchronicity and linear power delivery are exceptional, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
